gomodel:SYNGO_2538  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: The authors use immuno gold EM with well characterized epsin 1 antibody. Direct quote from the legend to figure 2 \"In the postsynaptic compartment, the epsin 1 immunolabeling was found in various locations, some near the postsynaptic density (Fig. 2D,E,G) but other scattered throughout the cytoplasm (Fig. 2F)\".. Experimental description: From the methods, \"Brain tissues from three rats (35 days old) were processed for immunogold labeling....\"" ;
